<dl id="n42015g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42015g">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42015g"> 15(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Legislatures, I / ask it?</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Chapter VI Auricular confession destroys all the sacred ties of marriage and human society.]</font> Legislators of the so-called Christian and civilized nations! I ask it again from you, &ldquo;Where is your consistency, your justice, your love of public morality, when you punish so severely the man who has sold the questions put to the woman in the confessional, while you honour and let free &hellip; the men whose public and private life is spent in spreading the very same moral poison &hellip; under the mask of religion?&rdquo; <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 68</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
